                                <div class="col-md-7 col-lg-6 ">
                                    <div class="detail-box">
                                        <h1>
                                            DTH Recharge
                                        </h1>
                                        <p>
                                            DTH recharge is an important service that ensures uninterrupted access to television channels and entertainment. It allows users to renew or add channel packs to their DTH connection easily. With online DTH recharge services, users can recharge their accounts anytime without visiting a store. This method is fast, secure, and convenient, helping users enjoy their favorite TV shows, movies, sports, and news without any interruption.
                                        </p>
                                        <div class="btn-box">
